
To Build the GPIO module:
> make KERNEL_SOURCE=< Path to kernel source >

To Clean the GPIO module:
> make clean KERNEL_SOURCE=< Path to kernel source >

To Load the GPIO kernel Module:
> insmod GPIO_Interrupts_Kernel_Based.ko GPIO=XXX TYPE=Y
                Y : 
                                0 = None
                                1 = Rising
                                2 = Falling
                                3 = Assert High (level)
                                4 = Assert Low (level)
                XXX:
                                GPIO number

